{"tid":2054692,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"2020全球最宜居城市出爐！台北連續2年蟬聯「全球最適合居住城市」冠軍。","createTime":"2020-06-07T10:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T01:08:53.000Z","uid":33359,"like":50,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"57841e7df18811845858442e298170860c43e898","tid":2054692,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"為了讓各國人士可以互相交流，提供移居地所需的資訊，「InterNations」公司每年都會進行全球最適合居住城市相關調查，而在本次針對全球178個國家、超過2萬人的調查中，受訪者從82個城市裡，選出2020年世界最適合居住的城市是「台北」，贏過紐約、巴黎等多個世界知名的觀光大城。<br />\n<br />\n高品質的生活條件，讓台北從這次調查脫穎而出，超過9成受訪者對於它便利的交通、醫療健保感到滿意；也有人指出，台北雖是首都，但物價、生活成本相對較低，就有印度移民表示，「與日、韓、香港相比，台灣的生活費用便宜」；另外，還有96％的受訪者認為，在台北讓他們感到很安全。<br />\n<br />\n然而，台北在「求職」及「定居」兩項評分表現較差，主要是因為台北人多用中文或閩南語溝通，對初來乍到的外籍人士來說，理解上有一定的困難，但親切友好的態度，仍能打破語言的隔閡，有80%的受訪者認為台北人普遍友善，位居全球第4。<br />\n<br />\n而在此次調查中，除了台北以外，進入前5名的城市還有馬來西亞首都吉隆坡，越南胡志民市、新加坡的新加坡市及加拿大蒙特婁，紐約、巴黎則只排在第74以及78。"},{"pid":"c7a928327f24a34187ce392069b40f697b4149af","tid":2054692,"uid":65888,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"住台北，屌定仔，食氣炸鍋，最後用水牙線洗牙<br />\n<br />\n幾時喺台北開埋百里香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n印巴經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7129c98551e26b9ba47f4f2716e4aac152d1fa","tid":2054692,"uid":37524,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"有印度移民表示：好過番印度"},{"pid":"ca463ff04e2be8a1e9305ba3b47c92bd62183c56","tid":2054692,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7a928327f24a34187ce392069b40f697b4149af","tid":2054692,"uid":65888,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"住台北，屌定仔，食氣炸鍋，最後用水牙線洗牙<br />\n<br />\n幾時喺台北開埋百里香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n印巴經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"想住台東<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d9885e7a563b26230f5d279d8960ddd2e57ce7","tid":2054692,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca463ff04e2be8a1e9305ba3b47c92bd62183c56","tid":2054692,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7a928327f24a34187ce392069b40f697b4149af","tid":2054692,"uid":65888,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"住台北，屌定仔，食氣炸鍋，最後用水牙線洗牙<br />\n<br />\n幾時喺台北開埋百里香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n印巴經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"想住台東<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:04:14.000Z","msg":"學識耕田未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf12273b863f0df60232a221e67479712e9d0834","tid":2054692,"uid":4156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:04:42.000Z","msg":"除左多厹同bitch <br />\n台北真係唔錯"},{"pid":"b2b1809804d0b7845ac8124303f861c29d2191a4","tid":2054692,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ac7129c98551e26b9ba47f4f2716e4aac152d1fa","tid":2054692,"uid":37524,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"有印度移民表示：好過番印度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"是<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aec40fae7961c68a07191